Django Admin Interface:
========================

->Django ModelAdmin class :
---------------------------
-its a configuration class that tells django admin interface to how to
and mange a model in adimin panel
-simply ,for  customizing model classes in admin panel for
 specifying how to show and bhave in admin panel

 exclude:- used for specifying which field to not show in Admin
 -save_model():- its a hook(override point) that allow you to
 customize what happens when an object is saved from the admin
panel
     -request: current HTTP request object
     -obj: The actual instance of the model being created or edited.
     -form:The ModelForm instance used to edit the object in the admin panel
     -change:A boolean indicating whether this is a change (True) or a new object (False).
   




